Idea:
A time ago I searched on fpsbanana for a good blast door or something like that for one of my levels, I didnt find so much so I made this detailed and nice prefab door.

Information:
A lever activated blast door which has an alert sound and 2 alert lights and a special sealing.



Note:
You can use it or edit it for your levels etc., but if you do so please give credits :D

Hope you like it and have fun with it!

(this is my first prefab I uploaded)

Author:
